definition: healthy/to invigorate/to strengthen/to be good at/to be strong in
Zhuang ethnic group of Guangxi, the PRC's second most numerous ethnic group

sentences.english: Some cows and sheep looded healthier than others too.
sentences.chinese: 同樣的這裏的牛羊也比此外處所健壯。

sentences.english: A systematic robustness testing approach was proposed. First the RI-Pro of BGP was analyzed.
sentences.chinese: 提出了一種系統實現協議健壯性測試的新方法。

sentences.english: The stress test verified the robustness of the product during high system usage.
sentences.chinese: 壓力測試可以驗證產品在系統高使用率時的健壯性。

sentences.english: A big man can have bodily strength, but spiritual weakness.
sentences.chinese: 一個身材高大的人可能身體健壯，但可能精神脆弱。

sentences.english: Why is robust mouse rejuvenation the quickest route to curing human aging?
sentences.chinese: 爲什麼小鼠健壯返老還童是治癒人類老化的最快路線？

sentences.english: The older he gets, the stronger he looks.
He's so robust and never has a trace of weariness.
sentences.chinese: 他非常健壯，從不顯示一絲倦意。

sentences.english: Being athletic, Tom found the climb quite easy.
sentences.chinese: 由於身體健壯，湯姆覺得爬山很容易。

sentences.english: Mr. Dolittle attributes his good health to careful living.
sentences.chinese: 杜立德先生把自己健壯的體魄歸功於審慎的生活方式。

sentences.english: However, it would not affect the floral bud differentiation and florescence.
sentences.chinese: 補光後，植株健壯，但對花芽分化和花期影響不大。

sentences.english: He seems to be the most robust horse in the field.
sentences.chinese: 它可能是場子裏最健壯的馬。

sentences.english: The memory protection and share mechanism can improve the reliability of the system.
sentences.chinese: 通過存儲保護機制提高系統健壯性。

sentences.english: Code conventions can help in reducing the brittleness of programs.
sentences.chinese: 編程規範可以幫助程序員們增加程序的健壯性。

sentences.english: His eagerness will not avail against the fitness and skill of his opponent.
sentences.chinese: 他求勝心切，但這並不能反抗得住對手的健壯與技藝。

sentences.english: Old Mabel is still going strong and still working on his farm every day.
sentences.chinese: 老梅布爾依然很健壯，天天還在他的農場裏工作。

sentences.english: This is precisely what you want in a robust file format.
sentences.chinese: 這就是真正想在一個健壯的文件格式中所獲得的。

definition: obese/bloated/swollen (style)/(fig.) (of an organization) oversized or overstaffed
